author: Sophocles
message: A short saying oft contains much wisdom.
title: Thought of the day

author: Epictetus
message: Difficulties are things that show a person what they are.
title: Thought of the day

author: Honore de Balzac
message: When you doubt your power, you give power to your doubt.
title: Thought of the day

author: Ovid
message: The cause is hidden. The effect is visible to all.
title: Thought of the day
